text: Frederick McEvoy (4 July 1856 - 5 November 1913) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class cricket match for Victoria in 1877. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1856 births Category:1913 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:People from the Riverina Category:Melbourne Cricket Club cricketers
